{"tid":2357200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"副作用多達73種 國藥疫苗可致失禁","createTime":"2021-01-07T09:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T05:50:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e156b0d4a7a6e2b30457a6a38f6dafaee9adba6e","tid":2357200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:14:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210107/T2O7POJR4NA63AX6Y4ENJN6XNU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210107%2FT2O7POJR4NA63AX6Y4ENJN6XNU%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=32b7c398\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210107%2FT2O7POJR4NA63AX6Y4ENJN6XNU%2F&h=4304ec72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210107/T2O7POJR4NA63AX6Y4ENJN6XNU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n副作用多達73種 國藥疫苗可致失禁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/1OedOVUJhQrdU9M0_NXyXtO6l4E=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QB7YQZLUNFHVFJQJIZM66JJGCQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F1OedOVUJhQrdU9M0_NXyXtO6l4E%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQB7YQZLUNFHVFJQJIZM66JJGCQ.jpg&h=c9dfafbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■專家陶黎納形容國藥疫苗為世上最不安全的疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n國藥集團研製的中國首款武漢肺炎疫苗日前獲當局批准上市，惟據內地疫苗專家貼出的該款疫苗的說明書上，卻赫然列出一長串達73種副作用。其中哮喘、尿失禁、視力減退等，更是罕見於其他疫苗的副作用清單上。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：華禁世衞入武漢查疫源  譚德塞狠批：非常失望<br />\n<br />\n中國國藥集團旗下的中國生物公司滅活疫苗（Vero細胞），商品名稱「眾愛可維」，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地專家︰世上最不安全疫苗<br />\n<br />\n對於如此之長的副作用清單，陶黎納直言「看完倒吸了一口冷氣」；更形容「（國藥疫苗）一舉成為世界上最不安全的疫苗」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查其他各款武漢肺炎疫苗資料，多顯示有注射部位疼痛、頭痛、疲倦等副作用，而今次國藥疫苗被曝光的副作用清單，除了以上其他疫苗常見的副作用外，卻整整多出近50種副作用。陶黎納表示，「沒有任何一種現役疫苗的不良反應種類數能超過眾愛可維，而且陶醫生可以斷定眾愛可維的不良反應種類數，絕對是前無古人後無來者，一騎絕塵」。此外，陶又指出，牛痘疫苗發明以來220年間，沒有任何一種疫苗出現過高血壓這種不良反應，結果中國疫苗拿下了世界紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n微博/中央社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eK9mh7YXBsvyzXQqCiM8f9jvmqM=/1356x570/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TM3GQF4GWBCP7H43XVF45EWMT4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FeK9mh7YXBsvyzXQqCiM8f9jvmqM%3D%2F1356x570%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTM3GQF4GWBCP7H43XVF45EWMT4.gif&h=357ab3c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"426c10dc2b04aee936f200947cab31a583743dc2","tid":2357200,"uid":27411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:21:42.000Z","msg":"Tvb話美/德/英國疫苗都好多副作用架，我就覺得中國疫苗最好，應該比站喺最前線最辛苦既紀律部隊率先接種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b8adb90ad857f3e8d94f94e549cfe256e57067","tid":2357200,"uid":29167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:22:04.000Z","msg":"打咗仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e90ca62f514272d99d4c6fd11b20eb8b7795b6c5","tid":2357200,"uid":307265,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"印度神童又講中咗"},{"pid":"c8c4747d131c3563f536b99a4dd2c2c9a92fe832","tid":2357200,"uid":286131,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又腹瀉又便秘<br />\n打和啦super，支拿又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0bf556e9612116a44ddf4d9e3283b35c52165e5","tid":2357200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T09:24:45.000Z","msg":"絕對是前無古人後無來者，一騎絕塵"},{"pid":"30b396aca55f0e7590792b2527c82d21c26b8b6b","tid":2357200,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"